      "Je ne me laisse pas faire",
      "La culture c'est la France",
      "Qu'ils viennent me chercher"
    ],
    "combo_partners": "Sarkozy (the controversial duo returns), Zemmour (two media magnets who love attention), Macron (elitist culture vs populist culture clash)",
    "target_audience": "Anti-elitist voters, culture war participants, anyone exhausted by political theatrics",
    "traits": [
