    "bio": "The man who detonated a bomb inside his own party: as LR president, he stunned France in June 2024 by unilaterally announcing an alliance with Le Pen's RN for the snap legislative elections, splitting LR in two. Expelled from the party (which he contested in court), he formed the 'À Droite!' group in the Assembly with fellow RN-allied defectors, and later launched the UDR (Union des Droites pour la République) movement. His betrayal became the defining moment of the 2024 political crisis on the right, permanently fracturing the Gaullist legacy party. Whether he's a traitor or a prophet depends entirely on whether RN wins in 2027—if they do, he'll claim he saw it coming first.",
