  "bardella": {
    "name": "Jordan Bardella",
    "role": "Président du Rassemblement National",
    "party": "Rassemblement National",
    "bio": "The 30-year-old RN president who went from TikTok sensation to France's most likely next president practically overnight. He led RN to a historic first-place finish in the June 2024 European elections (triggering Macron's disastrous dissolution), then positioned himself as PM candidate during the snap legislative elections—only to fall short when the left-wing 'republican front' blocked RN in the second round. A November 2025 Odoxa poll made headlines by predicting he would WIN the 2027 presidential election against any opponent. With Le Pen's March 2025 conviction and five-year office ban (under appeal), Bardella has accelerated his positioning as her successor, with the Le Pen-Bardella 'operation succession' officially launched in late 2025. Born in Seine-Saint-Denis to Italian immigrants, he's the child of immigration leading the anti-immigration party—an irony his opponents never tire of pointing out.",
